```class Solution {
    public int minFlipsMonoIncr(String s) {
        int flips = 0, ones = 0;
        for (char c : s.toCharArray()) {
            if (c == '1') ones++;
            flips = Math.min(flips + 1, ones);
        }
        return flips;
    }
}```
